      "widgets_values": [
        "To test it out select the VFI node.  Press ctrl-b to bypass it.  This will disable the smoothing and let you see the raw image output.\n\nThe numbers to adjust here are.\n\n* RFI node. multiplier.  Make higher for smoother transition between frames.\n* KSampler denoise.  Too low and you'll get a cartoony picture, too high and it'll replace the previous image\n* latent blend. Too low and the image eventually becomes single color / dark\n\nReconnect the VFI nodes to RIFE if you run out of memory to run GIMM."
